# Agent workflow — sprint working artifacts (ephemeral planning chatter)
# RCAs and templates ARE committed; everything else is working docs
# These patterns cover both the old docs/sprints/ location and the new
# docs/initiatives/INIT-XXX/sprints/ location.

# Sprint artifacts (old location — kept for backwards compatibility)
docs/sprints/sprint-*/scope.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/tech-review-*.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/sprint-plan.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/vp-eng-review.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/dev-report.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/product-review.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/test-eval.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/test-results.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/demo-output.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/security-review.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/compliance-review.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/infra-review.md
docs/sprints/sprint-*/cicd-review.md

# Sprint artifacts (new location — within initiatives)
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/scope.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/tech-review-*.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/sprint-plan.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/vp-eng-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/dev-report.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/product-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/test-eval.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/test-results.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/demo-output.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/security-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/compliance-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/infra-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/cicd-review.md

# Merge review artifacts (generated by request-merge.sh)
docs/initiatives/*/merge-review/diff-summary.md
docs/initiatives/*/merge-review/eng-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/merge-review/prod-acceptance.md
docs/initiatives/*/merge-review/security-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/merge-review/compliance-review.md
docs/initiatives/*/merge-review/devops-review.md

# Sprint template copies (generated by start-sprint.sh)
docs/initiatives/*/sprints/sprint-*/*.template

# Agent workflow — private domain context (sensitive project knowledge)
docs/personas/context/*.md
!docs/personas/context/README.md

# Project concerns are committed (they're project-level facts, not secrets)
# docs/personas/concerns/*.md is tracked

# Templates are always committed
!docs/initiatives/_templates/**
!docs/sprints/_templates/**
!docs/backlog/bugs/bug-report-template.md

# macOS
.DS_Store
